      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4032 - Yunus ibn Abd al-Rahman narrated from more than one person, from Abu Abdullah (as), regarding a man who trades with another man over something.\nImam (as) said: \"There is no harm, as long as the origin of the item is lawful.\""
